180316084200/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-38285223" about="#mwt326" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Webarchive","href":"./Template:Webarchive"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"https://web.archive.org/web/20180316084200/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-38285223"},"date":{"wt":"2018-03-16"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwA8c">Archived</a><span about="#mwt326" id="mwA8g"> 2018-03-16 at the </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Wayback_Machine" title="Wayback Machine" about="#mwt326" id="mwA8k">Wayback Machine</a><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:Webarchive_template_wayback_links" about="#mwt326" id="mwA8o"/> <i id="mwA8s"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./BBC" title="BBC" id="mwA8w">BBC</a></i></span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTESeligmanCsikszentmihalyi2000-108" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTESeligmanCsikszentmihalyi2000-108"><a href="./Happiness#cite_ref-FOOTNOTESeligmanCsikszentmihalyi2000_108-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTESeligmanCsikszentmihalyi2000-108" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Happiness#CITEREFSeligmanCsikszentmihalyi2000" id="mwA80">Seligman <span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwA84">&amp;</span> Csikszentmihalyi 2000</a>.</span></li></ol></div></div>

